Children.Description: A high-quality Mixture of Experts (MoE) model with open weights by Mistral AI.

Children.Name: llava
Children.Description: 🌋 LLaVA is a novel end-to-end trained large multimodal model that combines a vision encoder and Vicuna for general-purpose visual and language understanding. Updated to version 1.6.

Children.Name: neural-chat
Children.Description: A fine-tuned model based on Mistral with good coverage of domain and language.

Children.Name: codellama
Children.Description: A large language model that can use text prompts to generate and discuss code.

Children.Description: An uncensored, fine-tuned model based on the Mixtral mixture of experts model that excels at coding tasks. Created by Eric Hartford.

Children.Name: mistral-openorca

Children.Name: qwen
Children.Description: Qwen 1.5 is a series of large language models by Alibaba Cloud spanning from 0.5B to 72B parameters
